  "body": "If you've experienced a bug, please provide the following information:\r\n\r\n### Description of the Issue\r\n\r\nIn the View & Send tab, when a user has the currency to send set to an ERC-20 token and entered a value in \"Amount\", then changes the currency to ETH, the \"Amount\" value won't get reset.\r\n\r\nThe expected behavior is that the \"Amount\" value will be reset when the currency is changed. This is what happens when the currency is set to ETH with a value in \"Amount\", then changing the currency to an ERC-20 token.\r\n\r\nThis lack of consistency can make for accidental erroneous transactions.\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n![Steps to Reproduce](https://i.imgur.com/5AIx6d5.gif)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Description of Your Machine\r\n\r\nThis issue can be found in both the website and desktop application on every machine.\r\n\r\n### Console Logs / Screenshots\r\n\r\nSee Steps to Reproduce",
